Madeline Luciano was fired from PS 18 in Manhattan . 
  She allegedly allowed pupils to write nasty words about a 13-year-old girl on the board . 
  The girl was described as 'ugly', 'annoying' and 'phony' on the blackboard . 
  Ms Luciano claims she was trying to teach pupils about the evils of bullying . 
  She was fired after an investigation and claims she is the victim of 'injustice'